OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, frequent and
OL,7,Fprolonged in places, with
OL,8,Fthunderstorms possible in the north.
OL,9,FFurther showers overnight mixed with
OL,10,Fclear spells, before turning more
OL,11,Fgenerally wet later. Breezy at times
OL,12,Fand staying rather windy in coastal
OL,13,Fregions. Mild.
OL,14,
OL,15,CThursday:FA wet start for many, then
OL,16,Fbrighter with scattered heavy and
OL,17,Flocally thundery showers. Cool and
OL,18,Fblustery with strong winds in exposed
OL,19,Fspots but warm when the sunshine comes
OL,20,Fout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
